{
  "stem": "9987.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And according to the information we received, the train went in to Belzec, which was not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just a [NON-ENGLISH] camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That means the trains came in there--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A death camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trains came in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gassed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There burned them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there-- and there is no witness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never heard about a single witness that can testify that he was in Belzec and came out alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my suspicion is that that's where the rest of my-- my family is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's why it could happen between the 10th of August, and the 15th of August.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how long it took there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I-- at that-- on the Jewish calendar, the 10th of August was Tisha B'Av, which is a-- a day of Jewish memorial of the-- of the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of the destruction of the Jewish temple.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I celebrate our anniversary, our yahrzeit, what they say every year on Tisha B'Av for my whole family, for everybody that was there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To continue with my story, we were going on like that, every day to work, back and forth, until a couple months later.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes in October, the four brothers were called to the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [INAUDIBLE] and they ordered us that the SS, which had-- which had a training camp in a place called Moderowka, which was 20 kilometers away, 18 kilometers away, they want to get 30 tailors to their camp, to make uniforms for the SS.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they want all the four Bergers to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I did not intend to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we started to argue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, we got to finish our work for the Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We finally made a settlement.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
